title: Corelli Concerto grosso opus 6 n 8 - 44 lossless recordings
description:
44 lossless recordings of Corelli Concerto grosso opus 6 no. 8 "Fatto per la notte di Natale". Flac/Ape in separate tracks, log, scans, score. Addedd BBC "Building a library" broadcast about Corelli's opus 6. Enjoy!
